WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:45.400

00:01:48.705 --> 00:01:50.305
Freeze! Stop right there!

00:01:50.865 --> 00:01:52.905
Stay where you are!
Move again, and I'll shoot!

00:01:52.985 --> 00:01:54.385
Don't shoot! Please!

00:01:54.465 --> 00:01:56.025
We surrender!

00:01:56.105 --> 00:01:57.465
‎My goodness.

00:02:00.505 --> 00:02:04.945
DIE

00:02:23.945 --> 00:02:25.065
What are you laughing at?

00:02:25.825 --> 00:02:26.665
Enjoy the foot-soaking water?

00:02:43.025 --> 00:02:43.745
Officer He. We…

00:02:43.825 --> 00:02:45.825
-We met before.
-We met before.

00:02:45.905 --> 00:02:48.265
Do I know you? Did I arrest you before?

00:02:48.345 --> 00:02:50.185
-Yesterday afternoon. Yesterday afternoon.
-Afternoon.

00:02:50.265 --> 00:02:52.145
-I just saw you.
-We met.

00:02:53.385 --> 00:02:54.745
TRANSFORM BUSINESS FOR GROWTH

00:02:58.825 --> 00:03:00.025
You work for Jin Manshan?

00:03:00.945 --> 00:03:02.345
Then why didn't you
tell the truth yesterday?

00:03:02.425 --> 00:03:04.425
Are you involved
with the missing father and daughter?

00:03:05.025 --> 00:03:06.145
Nothing to do with us!

00:03:06.225 --> 00:03:08.225
-We just came here to take a look.
-We are just…

00:03:08.305 --> 00:03:08.985
What does that have to do with anything?

00:03:09.065 --> 00:03:09.985
-Nothing.
-Nothing.

00:03:10.065 --> 00:03:11.145
Shut up!

00:03:11.225 --> 00:03:12.265
One at a time.

00:03:12.905 --> 00:03:13.985
You go first.

00:03:14.065 --> 00:03:15.425
We… We're just…

00:03:16.105 --> 00:03:18.065
-We're just part-timers.
-Part-timers.

00:03:18.145 --> 00:03:19.585
Part-timers?

00:03:19.665 --> 00:03:20.665
What kind of "part-timers"
walk around with tattoos

00:03:20.745 --> 00:03:21.985
and carry stuff like that?

00:03:22.065 --> 00:03:23.625
We don't know anything.

00:03:23.705 --> 00:03:26.145
We just spent 200 yuan to get the tattoos,

00:03:26.225 --> 00:03:28.065
so we could go collect debts.

00:03:28.145 --> 00:03:29.505
You came here to collect money?

00:03:30.545 --> 00:03:32.425
How much does the Xu family
owe Jin Manshan?

00:03:32.505 --> 00:03:34.145
Two hundred and fifty thousand.

00:03:34.665 --> 00:03:35.545
How much did they actually borrow?

00:03:37.385 --> 00:03:38.425
Eight thousand.

00:03:40.865 --> 00:03:44.345
You loan sharks are real math geniuses.

00:03:46.745 --> 00:03:48.425
This isn't your first time here, is it?

00:03:48.505 --> 00:03:49.545
Yesterday afternoon.

00:03:49.625 --> 00:03:51.385
-Afternoon.
-We came yesterday afternoon.

00:03:51.465 --> 00:03:56.385
DIE

00:03:56.465 --> 00:03:57.305
Are you sure?

00:03:57.905 --> 00:03:58.785
No one is home.

00:03:58.865 --> 00:04:00.465
What's the point of writing that?

00:04:00.545 --> 00:04:02.065
You're so clueless.

00:04:02.145 --> 00:04:04.145
I wrote this to show Mr. Jin.

00:04:05.105 --> 00:04:06.425
Sling it over your shoulder. Quick.

00:04:22.265 --> 00:04:25.225
DAJIANCHANG NEIGHBORHOOD

00:04:25.905 --> 00:04:27.385
-I'm hungry.
-How about

00:04:27.465 --> 00:04:30.065
we go grab something to eat?

00:04:40.345 --> 00:04:41.585
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

00:04:42.465 --> 00:04:46.025
-We went out to get some tofu pudding.
-We ate tofu pudding.

00:04:46.105 --> 00:04:48.785
-Then we came back.
-We saw the tape had been removed.

00:04:48.865 --> 00:04:50.065
-We thought the family had returned.
-We thought…

00:04:50.145 --> 00:04:51.385
Enough.

00:04:51.465 --> 00:04:52.705
Are you two performing crosstalk?

00:04:53.305 --> 00:04:54.145
When was the last time

00:04:54.225 --> 00:04:55.545
the father and daughter
were seen leaving home?

00:04:55.625 --> 00:04:58.745
People said it was the day
before Hong Kong, China's handover.

00:04:58.825 --> 00:05:00.185
Someone saw them leave,

00:05:00.265 --> 00:05:02.265
-and they never came back.
-Never came back.

00:05:03.625 --> 00:05:05.225
30TH, MONDAY

00:05:11.105 --> 00:05:12.625
Why did the Xu family borrow money?

00:05:13.545 --> 00:05:15.145
-Because…
-You answer.

00:05:15.225 --> 00:05:16.905
The daughter was devoted.

00:05:16.985 --> 00:05:18.465
She borrowed money to treat her father.

00:05:18.545 --> 00:05:20.185
Her father was in poor health.

00:05:20.265 --> 00:05:23.105
The medical bills
drained everything they had.

00:05:23.185 --> 00:05:24.065
What illness?

00:05:24.865 --> 00:05:25.705
No idea.

00:05:30.905 --> 00:05:32.625
-We don't know.
-We really don't know.

00:05:32.705 --> 00:05:33.625
We honestly don't know.

00:05:44.665 --> 00:05:45.825
You were carrying a gun just now.

00:05:45.905 --> 00:05:47.585
Did you file the paperwork to borrow it?

00:05:50.305 --> 00:05:53.345
FOR DRAMATIC EFFECT. DO NOT IMITATE

00:05:53.425 --> 00:05:54.465
What are you doing?

00:05:56.345 --> 00:05:57.545
What are you doing exactly?

00:05:58.505 --> 00:06:00.185
That's pure reflex.

00:06:00.265 --> 00:06:03.065
When criminals hear a gunshot,
they assume it's real.

00:06:03.705 --> 00:06:04.905
What?

00:06:05.865 --> 00:06:07.505
Reflex.

00:06:08.145 --> 00:06:10.265
A real cop using a fake fun?
And you're proud of it.

00:06:10.345 --> 00:06:11.905
As long as it works.

00:06:11.985 --> 00:06:13.585
You nearly scared me to death.

00:06:14.185 --> 00:06:16.465
The Xu father and daughter
might've gone to relatives to dodge debt.

00:06:16.545 --> 00:06:18.025
I want to check their household records.

00:06:18.105 --> 00:06:20.145
Do you know what time it is?
The registry office isn't open yet.

00:06:21.305 --> 00:06:23.385
Two more hours. I'll wait.

00:06:25.505 --> 00:06:28.105
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY

00:06:40.865 --> 00:06:43.385
You dressed like
some imperial envoy on tour.

00:06:43.465 --> 00:06:45.665
Chasing suspects
in leather shoes and slacks?

00:06:45.745 --> 00:06:47.305
That's not practical.

00:07:25.865 --> 00:07:28.385
Timing matters more than being early.

00:07:29.105 --> 00:07:30.145
Oh my!

00:07:35.625 --> 00:07:38.345
He Yuanhang, what happened to you?

00:07:38.945 --> 00:07:41.665
Paint. I brushed against it.

00:07:42.305 --> 00:07:43.505
Brushed against it?

00:07:44.065 --> 00:07:46.705
Looks like you fell into a paint vat.

00:07:46.785 --> 00:07:48.465
That's what being a detective is like.

00:07:48.545 --> 00:07:50.345
Dirty, exhausting, and rough.

00:07:50.425 --> 00:07:52.905
-You never know what tomorrow will bring.
-Go wash up.

00:07:53.505 --> 00:07:55.945
Dad, you've changed.

00:07:56.705 --> 00:07:59.105
Ever since you joined
the criminal department,

00:07:59.185 --> 00:08:01.345
you've been talking big.

00:08:02.425 --> 00:08:04.985
Kiddo, I promise you.

00:08:05.065 --> 00:08:06.985
I'll prove it soon enough.

00:08:11.745 --> 00:08:12.785
That hairstyle is cool.

00:08:12.865 --> 00:08:15.425
When I grow up, I want one like that too.

00:08:23.385 --> 00:08:28.545
MODERN LAW ENFORCEMENT
UNWAVERING POLICE EXCELLENCE

00:08:31.665 --> 00:08:33.264
-Morning, Captain Zhao, Captain Qu.
-Morning.

00:08:34.105 --> 00:08:35.144
Captain Zhao.

00:08:41.545 --> 00:08:44.105
The case in Binchuan District,
where four teenagers had gone missing,

00:08:44.185 --> 00:08:45.505
has been going on for almost two weeks.

00:08:45.585 --> 00:08:47.105
We still haven't found them.

00:08:47.185 --> 00:08:49.505
All kinds of rumors are spreading online,

00:08:49.585 --> 00:08:51.465
and it's causing quite a stir.

00:08:51.545 --> 00:08:52.905
-Director Zou mentioned…
-I know.

00:08:52.985 --> 00:08:54.385
He already called me.

00:08:54.465 --> 00:08:56.465
We'll be assisting the municipal bureau
on this joint case.

00:08:56.545 --> 00:08:59.625
-Qu. You take this case.
-Alright.

00:08:59.705 --> 00:09:00.545
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

00:09:00.625 --> 00:09:03.265
Contact all stations in our jurisdiction.
Get them involved too.

00:09:03.345 --> 00:09:04.705
No problem.

00:09:04.785 --> 00:09:05.985
We all know each other. They'll cooperate.

00:09:06.065 --> 00:09:07.625
Report to me immediately
when there are any solid leads.

00:09:07.705 --> 00:09:08.625
Understood, Captain Zhao.

00:09:09.745 --> 00:09:10.825
Captain Zhao.

00:09:11.945 --> 00:09:13.945
-Good morning.
-Morning.

00:09:15.505 --> 00:09:18.105
Captain Zhao, about the report
I submitted earlier,

00:09:18.185 --> 00:09:20.265
when would you have time to approve it?

00:09:22.105 --> 00:09:23.105
What report?

00:09:23.185 --> 00:09:25.505
The application for field duty.

00:09:29.745 --> 00:09:30.585
Xiaohe,

00:09:31.305 --> 00:09:33.425
field work is tough,

00:09:33.505 --> 00:09:35.025
exhausting, and dangerous.

00:09:35.105 --> 00:09:36.665
Captain Zhao, I'm not afraid.

00:09:36.745 --> 00:09:38.225
I studied criminal investigation
for six years.

00:09:38.305 --> 00:09:39.665
Fieldwork is exactly what I'm trained for.

00:09:44.425 --> 00:09:45.265
Oh, well.

00:09:46.265 --> 00:09:48.185
If only you showed that same dedication

00:09:48.265 --> 00:09:50.705
to taking care of your dad.

00:09:51.225 --> 00:09:52.305
-Captain Zhao.
-But…

00:09:52.385 --> 00:09:54.065
The report you requested is ready.

00:09:56.345 --> 00:09:57.585
Come with me.

00:09:57.665 --> 00:09:59.785
Does Han Zi'ang have a phone or a camera?

00:09:59.865 --> 00:10:01.105
No.

00:10:02.065 --> 00:10:04.145
There's not much to do at Yuanlongli.

00:10:04.225 --> 00:10:06.545
People mostly go there
to take photos and videos.

00:10:06.625 --> 00:10:08.585
If your child doesn't have
a phone or a camera,

00:10:08.665 --> 00:10:09.585
it's unlikely he went there.

00:10:10.185 --> 00:10:11.945
Here's what you do.
Go home and wait for now.

00:10:12.025 --> 00:10:13.545
Maybe he skipped class
and went out to play.

00:10:13.625 --> 00:10:15.305
That's impossible.

00:10:15.385 --> 00:10:17.065
I met a psychic this morning.

00:10:17.145 --> 00:10:20.185
He said Ang must be in Yuanlongli.

00:10:20.265 --> 00:10:22.585
A psychic? That's all nonsense.

00:10:22.665 --> 00:10:24.345
Why would a psychic lie?

00:10:24.425 --> 00:10:26.265
He promised to help me find my child.

00:10:26.345 --> 00:10:29.625
Ma'am, what did this psychic look like?

00:10:29.705 --> 00:10:30.905
He…

00:10:30.985 --> 00:10:32.345
He is about this tall,

00:10:32.425 --> 00:10:34.945
wearing a colored shirt,
and carrying a bag.

00:10:35.025 --> 00:10:37.025
He said all the missing kids in Yuanlongli

00:10:37.105 --> 00:10:38.345
were found by him.

00:10:43.425 --> 00:10:44.505
Han Zi'ang.

00:10:45.665 --> 00:10:47.065
Come out.

00:10:47.145 --> 00:10:49.105
Your mom's looking for you.

00:10:51.665 --> 00:10:53.665
Now that Yuanlongli
is about to be demolished,

00:10:54.545 --> 00:10:57.425
everything hidden inside
will come out into the open.

00:11:01.105 --> 00:11:04.465
DEMOLITION

00:11:16.785 --> 00:11:20.385
You see,
if you hadn't gone to Beijing back then,

00:11:21.025 --> 00:11:22.545
would things between you two…

00:11:22.625 --> 00:11:23.825
No.

00:11:27.025 --> 00:11:28.345
And there's no "if".

00:11:31.065 --> 00:11:32.905
I've always wondered.

00:11:33.505 --> 00:11:35.185
You two were such a good match.

00:11:35.785 --> 00:11:37.665
What happened in the end?

00:12:14.825 --> 00:12:16.425
Where did the trike go?

00:12:19.025 --> 00:12:20.105
What trike?

00:12:20.625 --> 00:12:22.025
Are you remembering it wrong?

00:12:23.225 --> 00:12:24.505
No way.

00:12:24.585 --> 00:12:27.105
It was blocking the door.
I moved it myself.

00:12:35.225 --> 00:12:36.825
Someone must've been here.

00:12:36.905 --> 00:12:39.065
-Let's go back and check.
-Sir.

00:13:25.385 --> 00:13:27.465
MISSING PERSON

00:13:35.225 --> 00:13:36.105
You're here.

00:13:39.345 --> 00:13:40.505
What are you doing here?

00:13:42.585 --> 00:13:44.905
What kind of question is that?
I'm here to work.

00:13:46.025 --> 00:13:47.305
Did you track down
their household registration?

00:13:49.945 --> 00:13:51.785
The Xu's have two relatives in Weiyang.

00:13:51.865 --> 00:13:54.145
Xu Zhihong has a sister. Xu Meng
has an uncle on her mother's side.

00:13:54.225 --> 00:13:55.905
XU MEIQIN'S AND QIAO GUOQIANG'S ADDRESSES

00:13:58.825 --> 00:14:00.745
Let's split up. Make it quick.

00:14:06.025 --> 00:14:08.905
I don't have a brother like that.
And no niece either.

00:14:11.825 --> 00:14:15.185
Xu Meng borrowed money from you
to treat her father, right?

00:14:15.265 --> 00:14:18.185
To be honest, in my brother's condition,

00:14:18.265 --> 00:14:19.785
he'd be better off dead.

00:14:19.865 --> 00:14:20.905
It's done.

00:14:23.345 --> 00:14:25.225
-Alright. Have a nice day.
-Thank you.

00:14:26.945 --> 00:14:29.705
He couldn't pay the debt,
so he kept pestering me.

00:14:29.785 --> 00:14:33.065
Look around. This place is a mess.

00:14:33.145 --> 00:14:35.505
When was the last time you saw them?

00:14:35.585 --> 00:14:37.985
Last year, one night.
He suddenly had an attack.

00:14:38.065 --> 00:14:40.185
Meng brought him over to borrow money.

00:14:41.865 --> 00:14:43.145
Aunt.

00:14:44.305 --> 00:14:46.265
Open the door, Aunt.

00:14:46.785 --> 00:14:47.785
Aunt.

00:14:47.865 --> 00:14:48.905
Aunt.

00:14:49.745 --> 00:14:52.625
-Meng.
-Aunt, my dad's sick again.

00:14:56.145 --> 00:14:57.265
Slow down.

00:15:05.505 --> 00:15:07.745
Aunt, could you…

00:15:18.145 --> 00:15:19.385
Thank you, Aunt.

00:15:21.145 --> 00:15:21.985
Meng.

00:15:24.025 --> 00:15:26.625
I'm planning to move away soon.

00:15:27.625 --> 00:15:28.825
Where are you moving to?

00:15:41.425 --> 00:15:42.705
I understand.

00:15:42.785 --> 00:15:44.665
I won't come again.

00:15:44.745 --> 00:15:48.385
I'll find a way to pay you back.

00:15:56.665 --> 00:15:58.705
Take this. Go to the hospital now.

00:15:59.225 --> 00:16:00.385
Thank you, Aunt.

00:16:12.345 --> 00:16:14.025
She's a good kid.

00:16:15.025 --> 00:16:16.985
Definitely.

00:16:18.425 --> 00:16:19.345
What a shame.

00:16:19.425 --> 00:16:21.785
She got dragged down by her father.

00:16:24.785 --> 00:16:26.065
To be frank,

00:16:26.145 --> 00:16:28.025
when I heard my brother had gone missing,

00:16:28.105 --> 00:16:32.585
I actually felt relieved.

00:16:33.345 --> 00:16:36.145
I shouldn't have felt that way.

00:16:39.065 --> 00:16:41.065
Life and death aren't up to us.

00:16:41.145 --> 00:16:43.185
Not up to us?

00:16:43.265 --> 00:16:45.945
He brought this on himself.

00:16:46.025 --> 00:16:48.065
He was perfectly fine before.

00:16:48.145 --> 00:16:48.985
But two summers ago,

00:16:49.065 --> 00:16:51.265
he and his daughter
went to Mount Wu for a trip,

00:16:51.345 --> 00:16:53.465
like they were possessed.

00:16:54.065 --> 00:16:55.585
They ran into an accident
in the mountains.

00:16:55.665 --> 00:17:00.585
He fell off a cliff
and ended up like this.

00:17:00.665 --> 00:17:03.065
Half dead.

00:17:03.145 --> 00:17:05.985
A mountain accident?
The Mount Wu incident?

00:17:06.065 --> 00:17:08.224
MAJOR MOUNTAIN ACCIDENT HIT MOUNT WU
KUNHAI CITY, YESTERDAY

00:17:08.305 --> 00:17:10.424
It started with heavy rain,
then thick fog.

00:17:10.505 --> 00:17:13.625
That tour group got lost
the moment they entered the mountains.

00:17:13.704 --> 00:17:15.184
You can imagine. In the mountains,

00:17:15.265 --> 00:17:17.145
there was no food, no water,

00:17:17.665 --> 00:17:18.944
and no one coming to help.

00:17:19.944 --> 00:17:21.704
Many people froze to death.

00:17:22.224 --> 00:17:23.865
My uncle was one of the lucky ones.

00:17:23.944 --> 00:17:25.385
He made it out alive.

00:17:25.464 --> 00:17:26.704
He might as well be dead!

00:17:31.385 --> 00:17:34.065
That's how Xu Zhihong
ended up with his condition.

00:17:37.625 --> 00:17:40.345
-Can I borrow this newspaper?
-Take that.

00:17:40.865 --> 00:17:42.345
Why are you keeping
that frigging paper anyway?

00:17:44.865 --> 00:17:47.705
When was the last time you saw Xu Meng?

00:17:48.305 --> 00:17:49.425
When?

00:17:49.945 --> 00:17:51.345
Heaven knows how long ago!

00:17:54.065 --> 00:17:56.625
Officer, want me to pour you some tea?

00:18:20.065 --> 00:18:21.825
Does anyone in your family do this too?

00:18:23.265 --> 00:18:24.225
No, I just like it.

00:18:31.105 --> 00:18:32.065
Young man,

00:18:32.785 --> 00:18:35.465
do you think people are afraid
of dying at the end?

00:18:38.785 --> 00:18:40.145
I don't really know.

00:18:40.905 --> 00:18:42.185
Look at my brother-in-law.

00:18:42.265 --> 00:18:43.665
He can barely breathe.

00:18:43.745 --> 00:18:45.305
Living like that is worse than dying.

00:18:45.385 --> 00:18:48.025
So why keep him alive?

00:18:48.105 --> 00:18:49.865
Last winter, I cut ties with them.

00:18:50.465 --> 00:18:51.945
Just to keep him alive,

00:18:52.025 --> 00:18:53.425
the father and daughter scammed people.

00:18:53.505 --> 00:18:55.585
She even turned to prostitution
and worked as a hostess.

00:18:55.665 --> 00:18:58.585
Anyone tied to relatives like that
is doomed.

00:18:58.665 --> 00:18:59.945
Don't talk about Meng like that.

00:19:00.025 --> 00:19:01.145
Why not?

00:19:01.225 --> 00:19:02.825
Didn't Xu Meng take advantage of you?

00:19:03.345 --> 00:19:05.465
You lent her your wedding money.

00:19:05.545 --> 00:19:07.505
She said she'd pay it back
right away. Did she?

00:19:08.105 --> 00:19:09.985
And your engagement fell apart.

00:19:10.065 --> 00:19:11.425
You really don't know why?

00:19:25.545 --> 00:19:28.665
Do you know if they crossed
the wrong people?

00:19:30.105 --> 00:19:30.945
Probably loan sharks.

00:19:33.265 --> 00:19:34.465
My uncle is actually a good man.

00:19:34.545 --> 00:19:36.665
He raised Meng all by himself.

00:19:36.745 --> 00:19:38.185
It wasn't easy.

00:19:39.425 --> 00:19:41.825
So Xu Zhihong was a loving father?

00:19:41.905 --> 00:19:43.825
Loving, you say? More like a "treasure".

00:19:43.905 --> 00:19:45.905
He's in that state and still not dead.

00:19:45.985 --> 00:19:47.305
I'd say he's some treasure indeed.

00:19:47.385 --> 00:19:48.785
Dad!

00:19:52.425 --> 00:19:54.625
MAJOR MOUNTAIN ACCIDENT HIT MOUNT WU
KUNHAI CITY, YESTERDAY

00:19:54.705 --> 00:19:57.345
They survived an accident,
went into debt for treatment,

00:19:57.425 --> 00:19:59.065
and now someone hired a hit on them.

00:19:59.585 --> 00:20:01.705
The Xu's really have it rough.

00:20:01.785 --> 00:20:03.825
Let's just hope
nothing else happens to them.

00:20:06.625 --> 00:20:07.825
Hard to say.

00:20:07.905 --> 00:20:11.225
From the scene at their home,
they left in a hurry.

00:20:11.825 --> 00:20:14.465
But why would they go to Yuanlongli?

00:20:14.545 --> 00:20:16.825
And then disappear in the elevator?

00:20:17.785 --> 00:20:21.145
Something about this doesn't add up.

00:20:22.225 --> 00:20:23.465
Up till now,

00:20:23.545 --> 00:20:25.745
we still don't know how they disappeared.

00:20:27.145 --> 00:20:28.865
Let's hope nothing else happens to them.

00:20:28.945 --> 00:20:30.745
Otherwise, this case
could drag on forever.

00:20:36.145 --> 00:20:38.585
I'm heading to the video rental shop
Wolfie mentioned,

00:20:38.665 --> 00:20:39.505
see if I can dig up anything

00:20:39.585 --> 00:20:40.665
-about the person who hired the hit.
-Well.

00:20:40.745 --> 00:20:42.825
I think we should start
with the loan shark.

00:20:42.905 --> 00:20:44.985
Jin Manshan wasn't telling
the truth yesterday.

00:20:45.065 --> 00:20:46.585
He was definitely holding something back.

00:20:46.665 --> 00:20:48.545
We should press him
and get the truth out of him.

00:20:49.705 --> 00:20:51.505
Then you go find Jin Manshan.
I'll check out the video rental shop.

00:20:51.585 --> 00:20:54.545
That place is full of all kinds
of shady characters.

00:20:54.625 --> 00:20:56.705
Don't scare them off.

00:21:09.185 --> 00:21:10.185
Officer He.

00:21:11.145 --> 00:21:12.105
Hm?

00:21:13.745 --> 00:21:16.345
Actually, we can go together.

00:21:17.265 --> 00:21:18.985
Better to have each other's backs.

00:21:22.065 --> 00:21:23.425
That foot bath grossed you out that much?

00:21:24.825 --> 00:21:27.785
Sure. Call me "sir", and I'll go with you.

00:21:31.545 --> 00:21:33.345
He can't take a joke.

00:21:35.905 --> 00:21:38.105
WANXIANG VIDEO RENTAL SHOP

00:21:38.185 --> 00:21:40.945
CONTINUOUS SCREENINGS
NO ADDITIONAL TICKETS NEEDED

00:21:45.265 --> 00:21:46.425
RAN FANGXU POLICE ID

00:22:01.585 --> 00:22:04.025
Officers, this way, please.

00:22:04.105 --> 00:22:05.905
SCREENING ROOM

00:22:05.985 --> 00:22:08.665
TOP PICKS FROM HK
ACTION-PACKED WESTERNS

00:22:11.305 --> 00:22:12.545
The night before last,

00:22:12.625 --> 00:22:14.825
someone came in wearing a cap and a mask.

00:22:14.905 --> 00:22:15.785
Ring a bell?

00:22:17.225 --> 00:22:19.345
So many people come and go every day.

00:22:19.425 --> 00:22:20.905
How would I remember?

00:22:21.425 --> 00:22:23.825
Jin Manlang was here too.
You don't remember that either?

00:22:23.905 --> 00:22:25.305
I really don't know.

00:22:26.385 --> 00:22:28.505
We wouldn't dare mess
with those gangsters.

00:22:29.105 --> 00:22:29.945
You're lying.

00:22:30.025 --> 00:22:31.785
No way.

00:22:31.865 --> 00:22:34.265
How would I dare lie to you officers?

00:22:34.345 --> 00:22:35.985
-You!
-Hey.

00:22:36.065 --> 00:22:37.025
Ran.

00:22:37.105 --> 00:22:38.265
Come over.

00:22:48.345 --> 00:22:49.785
Nothing he says is true.

00:22:49.865 --> 00:22:51.825
He's just trying to get by.

00:22:51.905 --> 00:22:54.065
Pushing him won't help.
Everyone's got their struggles.

00:23:00.425 --> 00:23:01.545
This is a murder-for-hire case.

00:23:01.625 --> 00:23:02.905
Lives are on the line.

00:23:02.985 --> 00:23:05.825
If he won't cooperate,
I'll file for an investigation right now.

00:23:05.905 --> 00:23:07.385
Wait.

00:23:08.545 --> 00:23:09.505
Let me think.

00:23:11.145 --> 00:23:11.985
I'll think of a way.

00:23:29.865 --> 00:23:31.145
THE PLUM IN THE GOLDEN VASE

00:23:36.265 --> 00:23:37.225
This one looks interesting.

00:23:38.905 --> 00:23:40.305
I'll take it back
and watch it at the station.

00:23:41.265 --> 00:23:43.825
It talks about human desires.

00:23:43.905 --> 00:23:44.985
-Officer.
-What is it?

00:23:45.865 --> 00:23:48.265
Look at me. My head just cleared up.

00:23:48.345 --> 00:23:51.545
I do remember that guy wearing a mask.

00:23:52.145 --> 00:23:53.145
What did he look like?

00:23:53.225 --> 00:23:54.865
Black cap, white mask. Does that help?

00:23:56.265 --> 00:23:59.545
-How tall?
-I was sitting down. Couldn't tell.

00:23:59.625 --> 00:24:01.025
What was he watching?

00:24:01.105 --> 00:24:03.905
That's the strange part.
He didn't watch anything.

00:24:03.985 --> 00:24:05.025
He went straight to the back
after coming in.

00:24:05.105 --> 00:24:06.105
He said he was looking for the restroom.

00:24:06.185 --> 00:24:09.745
Then he talked to Wolf for a bit,
took a phone call, and left.

00:24:09.825 --> 00:24:11.625
How did he leave? Did he drive?

00:24:11.705 --> 00:24:13.305
I was sitting over there. I didn't see.

00:24:13.385 --> 00:24:14.385
You'd better be honest.

00:24:14.465 --> 00:24:16.225
I'm really good at faces.

00:24:18.025 --> 00:24:19.065
I really am.

00:24:22.745 --> 00:24:25.105
VIDEO RENTAL SHOP

00:24:35.985 --> 00:24:36.825
What's wrong?

00:24:37.865 --> 00:24:40.025
It won't help to worry.
Let's go find Jin Manshan.

00:24:41.065 --> 00:24:41.985
Get in.

00:25:22.025 --> 00:25:23.105
Mister.

00:25:24.585 --> 00:25:25.825
What is it?

00:25:31.225 --> 00:25:33.105
Please. What do you want?

00:25:33.185 --> 00:25:34.425
Relax.

00:25:35.785 --> 00:25:37.345
Just want to ask about someone.

00:25:37.425 --> 00:25:39.705
-Go on, please.
-Stay still.

00:25:51.585 --> 00:25:52.425
So many books.

00:25:53.665 --> 00:25:56.225
This is sold by weight.
We can get a good price for it.

00:26:10.945 --> 00:26:11.865
There's a ghost making noise.

00:26:17.465 --> 00:26:19.945
-Where?
-Over there.

00:26:53.425 --> 00:26:54.465
See it?

00:26:55.985 --> 00:26:58.505
You know, my memory's sharp.

00:26:59.345 --> 00:27:01.505
This is obviously
a drifters' resting spot.

00:27:02.025 --> 00:27:03.345
That doesn't prove anything.

00:27:04.145 --> 00:27:05.745
Why not?

00:27:05.825 --> 00:27:08.545
These two wooden stools
were on the 18th floor just now.

00:27:14.265 --> 00:27:16.785
Which means someone's been tailing us.

00:27:16.865 --> 00:27:17.825
Help!

00:27:18.465 --> 00:27:20.705
-Help!
-Help!

00:27:21.545 --> 00:27:23.225
-Help!
-Help!

00:27:23.305 --> 00:27:25.545
Don't come any closer!

00:27:26.185 --> 00:27:28.225
-Help…
-Help!

00:27:28.305 --> 00:27:30.305
Help…

00:27:30.905 --> 00:27:31.825
Stop!

00:27:34.545 --> 00:27:36.585
Sir! Sir!

00:27:48.745 --> 00:27:49.705
Ang!

00:27:50.705 --> 00:27:51.745
Ang!

00:27:52.785 --> 00:27:53.945
Ang!

00:27:54.465 --> 00:27:56.025
Is he okay?

00:27:56.545 --> 00:27:58.785
Ms. Wang, let's send
the boy to the hospital first.

00:27:58.865 --> 00:28:00.225
Quick. Get in.

00:28:00.305 --> 00:28:02.985
-What's going on with the victim?
-He's the suspect.

00:28:03.545 --> 00:28:04.665
These two are the victims.

00:28:04.745 --> 00:28:05.985
The kid attacked them with a knife.

00:28:06.065 --> 00:28:07.025
Good thing it was dull.

00:28:07.785 --> 00:28:08.865
Have you seen my dad?

00:28:10.545 --> 00:28:11.545
NEW YORK BLOCK

00:28:11.625 --> 00:28:14.425
-Dad, you're hurt too?
-Just a scratch. I'm fine.

00:28:15.465 --> 00:28:17.905
Where's Fangxu? He was just here.

00:28:24.825 --> 00:28:27.305
-Mr. He, are you alright?
-Just superficial.

00:28:27.385 --> 00:28:28.905
Xiaohe, take my car.

00:28:28.985 --> 00:28:30.145
Get your dad home to rest.

00:28:31.265 --> 00:28:32.665
I don't need you worrying about me.

00:28:33.465 --> 00:28:34.825
Who's worrying about you?

00:28:34.905 --> 00:28:36.385
Captain Zhao is taking us to the scene.

00:28:36.465 --> 00:28:37.585
Stop wandering around here.

00:28:38.185 --> 00:28:40.585
Jerk, I found the boy.

00:28:40.665 --> 00:28:42.105
What? Are you trying to take the credit?

00:28:42.185 --> 00:28:43.785
-Dad.
-No wonder you're bald.

00:28:45.225 --> 00:28:47.385
Living off other people's work.

00:28:50.025 --> 00:28:51.025
Ran!

00:28:52.745 --> 00:28:53.585
Ran!

00:28:54.625 --> 00:28:57.305
-Get in.
-Alright.

00:28:59.905 --> 00:29:00.745
Let's go.

00:29:32.985 --> 00:29:33.825
Why are we here?

00:29:34.905 --> 00:29:38.185
Isn't Jin Manshan's men
supposed to be at Jinsha Market?

00:29:39.545 --> 00:29:41.665
Being a beat officer takes skill.

00:29:41.745 --> 00:29:44.385
These 20 years weren't for nothing.

00:29:54.625 --> 00:29:57.105
LEIGONG STREET

00:30:03.345 --> 00:30:04.785
They've got a lookout.

00:30:09.465 --> 00:30:11.305
Play drunk. Can you do that?

00:30:19.305 --> 00:30:22.025
-I want more.
-Slow down.

00:30:22.105 --> 00:30:24.985
-Another carton.
-Watch the step. Slow down.

00:30:25.065 --> 00:30:27.025
I can drink another carton of beer.

00:30:27.745 --> 00:30:28.785
Wait.

00:30:28.865 --> 00:30:30.625
Why don't we just go in?

00:30:30.705 --> 00:30:31.545
Why make it so complicated?

00:30:32.145 --> 00:30:34.145
It's a small gambling den.

00:30:34.225 --> 00:30:36.265
I busted it before.

00:30:37.345 --> 00:30:39.425
This time, we'll just scare them a bit.

00:30:40.265 --> 00:30:42.545
-Slow down.
-I'm fine.

00:30:49.705 --> 00:30:51.305
His legs.

00:30:57.585 --> 00:30:59.025
Right here.

00:31:03.945 --> 00:31:06.025
Why is it you again, Officer He?

00:31:06.985 --> 00:31:07.945
Cut the crap.

00:31:08.025 --> 00:31:09.185
Is Jin Manshan inside?

00:31:10.505 --> 00:31:11.385
How many people?

00:31:12.305 --> 00:31:14.025
-Over 20.
-More than 20?

00:31:21.705 --> 00:31:22.545
Where are you going?

00:31:22.625 --> 00:31:23.665
Too many of them.

00:31:23.745 --> 00:31:25.505
We can't just rush in.
I need to check the layout first.

00:31:36.985 --> 00:31:38.705
Business looks pretty good lately.

00:31:39.225 --> 00:31:40.265
That's all the bosses.

00:31:40.345 --> 00:31:43.145
I just watch the door and keep lookout.

00:31:43.225 --> 00:31:46.345
Officer He,
please don't tell Mr. Jin it's me.

00:31:46.425 --> 00:31:49.465
You've got some nerve
to bargain with me, huh?

00:31:49.545 --> 00:31:50.905
If you have time, read a book.

00:31:50.985 --> 00:31:52.825
Or get a proper job in Guangzhou.

00:31:52.905 --> 00:31:54.825
Stop hanging around with these people.

00:31:54.905 --> 00:31:57.065
-Got it?
-Got it, Officer He.

00:32:04.745 --> 00:32:05.665
Listen up.

00:32:05.745 --> 00:32:08.265
When you go back in,
as soon as you hear a gunshot,

00:32:08.345 --> 00:32:10.185
shout "police are coming" four more times.

00:32:10.265 --> 00:32:12.065
Then hide. Stay out of sight
for a few days.

00:32:12.145 --> 00:32:13.545
When you come out,
just say you got detained.

00:32:13.625 --> 00:32:14.985
Understand?

00:32:15.065 --> 00:32:16.945
Officer He, you brought a gun?

00:32:17.025 --> 00:32:17.865
Mm.

00:32:17.945 --> 00:32:19.305
That's intense.

00:32:19.385 --> 00:32:21.305
Stop talking and move.

00:32:27.385 --> 00:32:29.505
There's a trash bin by the back door.

00:32:29.585 --> 00:32:32.665
I'll wait there
and catch anyone who slips out.

00:32:32.745 --> 00:32:35.385
You're taking the lead today.
Can you handle it?

00:32:35.465 --> 00:32:36.985
Don't just curry favor
with others all the time.

00:32:37.985 --> 00:32:40.545
If I hadn't carried his legs just now,
would you have handled it alone?

00:32:41.705 --> 00:32:43.305
Cut it out.

00:32:43.385 --> 00:32:45.265
Open fire when I'm in position.

00:32:47.225 --> 00:32:49.585
-What now?
-I've never seen Jin Manshan.

00:32:49.665 --> 00:32:51.025
What does he look like?

00:32:51.545 --> 00:32:54.585
Big gold chain around his neck.
Two gold teeth.

00:32:56.865 --> 00:32:58.545
Big gold chain. Gold teeth.

00:33:17.665 --> 00:33:19.065
Police are here!

00:33:20.345 --> 00:33:23.025
Police are here! Police!

00:33:23.105 --> 00:33:24.585
Police!

00:33:24.665 --> 00:33:26.625
Police are here!

00:33:43.505 --> 00:33:45.145
-Police are coming!
-Police are coming!

00:33:45.225 --> 00:33:47.865
-Run quickly. Police are coming!
-Police are here!

00:33:47.945 --> 00:33:50.265
-Run!
-Run quickly!

00:33:50.345 --> 00:33:51.665
Move it now!

00:33:52.705 --> 00:33:53.705
Big gold chain. Gold teeth.

00:34:13.784 --> 00:34:14.824
Jin Manshan!

00:34:15.465 --> 00:34:17.185
Not me. You got the wrong person.

00:34:28.385 --> 00:34:30.025
Police! Stay put!

00:34:33.025 --> 00:34:34.905
Stop running! Stand right there!

00:34:48.025 --> 00:34:50.145
Jin Manshan, stop!

00:34:50.225 --> 00:34:52.425
He Yuanhang! He Yuanhang!

00:34:53.945 --> 00:34:55.264
He Yuanhang!

00:35:00.585 --> 00:35:01.705
Stop running!

00:35:12.505 --> 00:35:14.905
Officer He, what is this?

00:35:14.985 --> 00:35:16.265
Why are you doing this?

00:35:16.345 --> 00:35:18.785
Also, what if the lamp post
leaks electricity?

00:35:18.865 --> 00:35:19.905
Cut the nonsense.

00:35:19.985 --> 00:35:21.905
Don't tell me you have no idea
why you're being cuffed.

00:35:21.985 --> 00:35:24.345
Yesterday afternoon,
when I asked about Xu Meng,

00:35:24.425 --> 00:35:25.545
why didn't you say anything?

00:35:25.625 --> 00:35:29.345
Officer He, I don't follow.

00:35:29.425 --> 00:35:30.785
Who is Xu Meng?

00:35:30.865 --> 00:35:32.625
She borrowed 8,000 from you.

00:35:32.705 --> 00:35:34.425
It has grown to 250,000 with interest.

00:35:34.505 --> 00:35:36.145
Does that jog your memory?

00:35:36.225 --> 00:35:37.625
I've got a lot of borrowers.

00:35:38.225 --> 00:35:40.825
I don't remember small fry like that.

00:35:40.905 --> 00:35:43.625
I only deal with big clients.

00:35:43.705 --> 00:35:45.145
Then why did you have
someone watching her house?

00:35:45.225 --> 00:35:48.105
Young man, you're really confusing me.

00:35:48.185 --> 00:35:50.425
I don't even know if Xu Meng
is a man or a woman.

00:35:50.505 --> 00:35:52.265
Why would I have someone watch her?

00:35:57.865 --> 00:36:00.225
Here. Take a look. Recognize this?

00:36:02.145 --> 00:36:04.225
I really have no idea.

00:36:04.305 --> 00:36:07.745
My guys handle small loans like 8,000.

00:36:08.545 --> 00:36:11.945
This wrench owes me money
and still runs off.

00:36:14.265 --> 00:36:15.865
Watch your mouth.

00:36:15.945 --> 00:36:17.545
She owes money and skips out.

00:36:17.625 --> 00:36:19.705
Why should I respect her?
Did she respect me?

00:36:19.785 --> 00:36:20.665
It's not even 10,000.

00:36:20.745 --> 00:36:23.345
She could've paid it back somehow.

00:36:23.425 --> 00:36:26.945
-Wrench. I'll catch her one day…
-Can't you talk without swearing?

00:36:27.025 --> 00:36:28.145
Huh?

00:36:29.265 --> 00:36:30.625
There you go again.

00:36:37.705 --> 00:36:38.705
You!

00:36:39.865 --> 00:36:42.705
Officer He, you're done asking.

00:36:42.785 --> 00:36:44.105
Let me ask you something.

00:36:46.225 --> 00:36:49.425
What did Jin Manlang do?

00:36:49.505 --> 00:36:51.225
Are you sure you don't know?

00:36:53.665 --> 00:36:56.785
Did that idiot run his mouth,
saying he killed someone?

00:36:57.505 --> 00:36:58.585
Don't believe him.

00:36:58.665 --> 00:37:00.545
He's been a coward since he was a kid.

00:37:00.625 --> 00:37:02.705
Too scared to kill a chicken,
and he talks about murder?

00:37:02.785 --> 00:37:04.385
He's just bluffing.

00:37:06.425 --> 00:37:08.105
You don't know your brother very well.

00:37:16.625 --> 00:37:17.745
Jin Manshan,

00:37:17.825 --> 00:37:19.625
you assaulted a police officer.

00:37:19.705 --> 00:37:21.345
I could detain you for that.

00:37:22.185 --> 00:37:23.265
But listen.

00:37:24.505 --> 00:37:27.385
If you can help me find out
what else the father and daughter

00:37:27.465 --> 00:37:29.785
were involved in,
besides borrowing from you,

00:37:29.865 --> 00:37:31.865
we'll count it as making up for it.

00:37:31.945 --> 00:37:33.305
Do you get what I mean?

00:37:33.985 --> 00:37:34.865
Yes.

00:37:41.705 --> 00:37:43.465
-Thank you.
-Hands.

00:37:44.785 --> 00:37:45.785
Don't forget that.

00:38:06.225 --> 00:38:07.385
Where are we going?

00:38:08.585 --> 00:38:09.865
I'll drop you back at the dorm.

00:38:11.505 --> 00:38:12.825
Let me off at a bus stop.

00:38:14.065 --> 00:38:16.305
It's late. There are no buses now.

00:38:22.345 --> 00:38:24.785
I've noticed you've been off today.

00:38:25.705 --> 00:38:27.625
I told you. Lack of sleep can mess you up.

00:38:27.705 --> 00:38:29.025
You never listen.

00:38:29.105 --> 00:38:31.745
Not enough sleep affects your judgment

00:38:31.825 --> 00:38:33.185
and makes you irritable.

00:38:34.105 --> 00:38:36.385
He was being disrespectful.
He had it coming.

00:38:49.665 --> 00:38:52.185
Pass me the stuff in the door handle.

00:39:00.545 --> 00:39:01.585
Stay-awake kit.

00:39:02.585 --> 00:39:04.105
My daughter got it for me.

00:39:09.305 --> 00:39:10.745
Your daughter sounds thoughtful.

00:39:11.785 --> 00:39:13.305
More than that.

00:39:13.825 --> 00:39:14.825
Want to try?

00:39:24.345 --> 00:39:26.225
Her teachers all say

00:39:26.745 --> 00:39:29.025
she takes after me.

00:39:29.785 --> 00:39:31.385
Quick-witted.

00:39:31.465 --> 00:39:33.705
The only problem is she's a bit stubborn.

00:39:34.385 --> 00:39:35.905
She's great at sports

00:39:35.985 --> 00:39:37.745
and loves figuring things out.

00:39:37.825 --> 00:39:38.985
Brains and brawn.

00:39:39.505 --> 00:39:40.585
Just like me.

00:39:41.465 --> 00:39:44.665
Do you think I should
let her join the police like me,

00:39:44.745 --> 00:39:47.145
or go into finance like her mom?

00:39:47.825 --> 00:39:49.345
Don't mind me talking so much.

00:39:49.425 --> 00:39:51.225
I'm driving at night.

00:39:51.305 --> 00:39:52.985
Talking keeps me awake.

00:39:54.305 --> 00:39:56.465
It's fine. Go on.

00:39:56.545 --> 00:39:59.385
Don't let me do the talking.
You say something too.

00:40:01.825 --> 00:40:03.225
Why did you come to Weiyang?

00:40:03.985 --> 00:40:05.545
My mom got married. I came with her.

00:40:07.265 --> 00:40:09.745
Right. You didn't finish
your story last time.

00:40:10.265 --> 00:40:12.425
What about you? What does your family do?

00:40:19.985 --> 00:40:21.585
Had a falling-out with them?

00:40:23.825 --> 00:40:27.185
You young people live so far from home.

00:40:27.945 --> 00:40:30.625
Your parents worry and nag a little.

00:40:30.705 --> 00:40:32.385
That's normal.

00:40:35.025 --> 00:40:36.345
They passed away.

00:41:23.985 --> 00:41:24.985
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:41:29.945 --> 00:41:31.105
Speak up.

00:41:31.185 --> 00:41:34.185
Mr. Jin, we were thinking
of staking out her place

00:41:34.265 --> 00:41:35.505
and handling it ourselves.

00:41:35.585 --> 00:41:36.625
Handling it yourselves?

00:41:37.585 --> 00:41:38.625
So, your solution

00:41:38.705 --> 00:41:41.945
is to let the police trace it back to me?

00:41:42.785 --> 00:41:43.825
-No. It's not like that.
-Mr. Jin.

00:41:43.905 --> 00:41:45.465
Mr. Jin. Mr. Jin.

00:41:46.825 --> 00:41:48.385
Mr. Jin, I brought him here.

00:41:48.465 --> 00:41:49.945
Morning, Mr. Jin.

00:41:50.945 --> 00:41:51.985
Get lost.

00:41:54.265 --> 00:41:55.305
Thank you.

00:41:55.385 --> 00:41:56.825
-Sit.
-Let's sit.

00:41:59.145 --> 00:42:01.785
What is the situation inside?
What did he say?

00:42:01.865 --> 00:42:04.025
Wolf is doing fine in there.
Food is decent.

00:42:04.105 --> 00:42:06.745
When he first got locked up,
he was bragging.

00:42:06.825 --> 00:42:07.705
He said he took out two people.

00:42:10.305 --> 00:42:12.825
How do you know he was bluffing?

00:42:12.905 --> 00:42:15.465
Mr. Jin, you know my nickname.

00:42:15.545 --> 00:42:16.585
Sharp Ears.

00:42:16.665 --> 00:42:19.585
When he first went in,
he clung to the bars and refused to move.

00:42:19.665 --> 00:42:21.345
He kept crying and told the warden

00:42:21.425 --> 00:42:22.985
that he didn't kill anyone.

00:42:23.065 --> 00:42:24.545
He only slaughtered a few chickens.

00:42:25.265 --> 00:42:26.105
Are you sure?

00:42:26.185 --> 00:42:28.545
Mr. Jin, I was locked up
for pickpocketing.

00:42:28.625 --> 00:42:30.705
If Wolf had killed someone,
he wouldn't be in the same place as me.

00:42:34.225 --> 00:42:36.465
You know the law pretty well.

00:42:37.345 --> 00:42:38.465
Thank you, Mr. Jin.

00:42:39.265 --> 00:42:40.185
By the way,

00:42:40.705 --> 00:42:42.625
the one who hired him,

00:42:44.345 --> 00:42:45.185
any news?

00:42:45.265 --> 00:42:47.345
Mr. Jin, I've sent people
to track him down.

00:42:49.785 --> 00:42:51.345
That dickhead.

00:42:53.345 --> 00:42:55.145
He set Manlang up.

00:42:55.825 --> 00:42:56.985
I'll make sure he pays for it.

00:42:57.065 --> 00:42:58.505
Yeah. Make him pay.

00:42:59.505 --> 00:43:00.345
Mr. Jin.

00:43:02.465 --> 00:43:03.505
What is it?

00:43:04.785 --> 00:43:06.665
The punk who set Wolf up

00:43:06.745 --> 00:43:07.785
has been found.

00:43:09.185 --> 00:43:10.145
Who is it?

00:43:10.225 --> 00:43:12.825
The video rental shop owner
didn't recognize him,

00:43:12.905 --> 00:43:13.945
but he remembers the car.

00:43:14.545 --> 00:43:16.985
A Mercedes. Plate ending in 688.

00:43:19.305 --> 00:43:20.865
688.

00:45:04.385 --> 00:45:08.065
PARKING GARAGE EXIT